00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:06,320
there's so many avatars, various avatars
it could be confusing, you know

82
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:13,180
so - as innumerable as the waves of the ocean - Vedavyas says in the beginning of the Bhagavatam

