scratch his back, because He's a turtle

146
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:15,280
even people go, Can you scratch
my back? - I can't reach that

147
00:17:15,290 --> 00:17:22,130
so what to speak of a turtle - even more
difficult.  So He's omnipotent and He

148
00:17:22,130 --> 00:17:26,990
can't scratch his own back. He's
omniscient he knows everything, so He

149
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:32,960
should know where the Earth is. How does he find the Earth? - Through the sense of smell

150
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:40,320
which is also in the Bhagavad-gita:
puṇyo gandhaḥ pṛthivyāḿ ca/ tejaś cāsmi vibhāvasau

151
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:45,360
jīvanaḿ sarva-bhūteṣu/ tapaś cāsmi tapasviṣu

