whimsical thought - there's a way to
connect this to Krishna conception

161
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:51,440
there's a way to connect everything to
Krishna conception

162
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:55,790
because there's only Krishna - actually
the fact of the matter

163
00:18:55,790 --> 00:19:00,480
there is only Krishna and by that we
mean Radha Krishna Lalita Vishaka

