00:19:09,170 --> 00:19:14,360
kingdom minister you know - when you say "the King"
a king doesn't live in isolation

166
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:25,180
neither does Krishna, so He is everything
ahaṁ sarvasya prabhavo

167
00:19:25,180 --> 00:19:30,880
"Everything comes from Me" and we go, 
"Well what about?.." - Everything comes from Me

168
00:19:30,890 --> 00:19:36,230
- Yeah, but what... - Everything comes from Me
right and if you see something that

169
00:19:36,230 --> 00:19:42,080
