00:20:11,340 --> 00:20:19,260
he's upset at the foulness of the situation

174
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:24,700
and, you know, it's a Bengali joke, but then what he's told is

175
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:29,980
but you're the cause of that
before - I was in another position before

176
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:37,220
and now by contact with you this is the
outcome - so to speak

177
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:45,000
