00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:08,200
that's mysterious
how did cit get converted into all this stuff

181
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:14,080
but still - so - puṇyo gandhaḥ the original fragrance

182
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:18,800
so through the sense of smell
He locates the Earth

183
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:22,920
that's what we're told - like
searching then traces it all the way to

